wiki.content: "That's What You Get" is the second Australian single, third U.S. single and the fourth UK single from the album Riot!. It is featured in the video game Rock Band 2 and was certified Gold in the United States on December 12, 2008, selling over 500,000 copies. track.name: That's What You Get
comments: I love Paramore but I really hate their new album. They have gone really commercial and pop like. Go back to doing albums like this and 'All We Know is Falling' and 'Brand New Eyes'. Please! It really frustrates me too because Paramore are coming to my hometown in september and they are the one band I have always wanted to see live. They will probably play most of the stuff on their new album.
i love this song brings back memories good ones
she is trying so hard let her in your heart see what you get
THAT'S WHAT YOU GET WHEN LET YOUR HEART WIN!!!! [22]
Excellent. Cannot wait for their new album. :)
